{"id": "art-216", "label": "Art. 216", "title": "Art. 216: Condiţii generale", "slug": "art-216", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 216: Condi&#355;ii generale </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale,\nprocurorul poate dispune luarea m&#259;surii controlului judiciar pe\ncau&#355;iune fa&#355;&#259; de inculpat, dac&#259; sunt întrunite\ncondi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 223 alin. (1) &#351;i (2), luarea\nacestei m&#259;suri este suficient&#259; pentru realizarea scopului\nprev&#259;zut la art. 202 alin. (1), iar inculpatul depune o cau&#355;iune a\nc&#259;rei valoare este stabilit&#259; de c&#259;tre organul judiciar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1072302849\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2205\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1072302849\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259;, în\nprocedura de camer&#259; preliminar&#259;, sau instan&#355;a de judecat&#259;,\nîn cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii, poate dispune luarea m&#259;surii controlului\njudiciar pe cau&#355;iune fa&#355;&#259; de inculpat, dac&#259; sunt\nîndeplinite condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1316338644\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2204\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1316338644\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 212-215<sup>1</sup> se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}